{"tid":268488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"月花萬元讓女學興趣班僅派第10志願 中國家長嫌太遠","createTime":"2017-06-03T05:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T12:15:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a661f0d84f0e56b264d38a6d0b8e20a73e27957e","tid":268488,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170603/large/1496457353_cd6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170603%2Flarge%2F1496457353_cd6d.jpg&h=7ac73f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小一統一派位結果今日揭盅，今年錄得逾3.2萬名學生參加派位，人數創近十年新高，競爭激烈下，教育局公佈67.6%人獲派首三志願，派位滿意率亦屬近三年最低。<br />\n<br />\n今早在北區一個專供跨境學童用的派位中心，9時已有逾200家長心急等待，有家長得悉子女被派到第一志願、鄰近關口學校喜極，也有未獲派心儀志願的家長痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n其中，排頭位的內地家長李太，是獲知派位結果的第一人，不過女兒被派到第10志願以後的非北區學校，難免失望，更不願透露被派到什麼地區及學校。家住福田的李太，曾出席被派學校簡介會，知道由關口坐校車直達學校，需時約1小時，但她覺得太遠。<br />\n<br />\n李太說已準備好履歷表及相關資料叩門用，打算往10幾間小學叩門，她目前月花1萬元讓女兒學舞蹈、鋼琴、書法、英文會話及繪畫。<br />\n<br />\n內地家長羅太亦失落派位，小孩被派到較遠的青衣區，她表示首志願是大埔官立小學，她指雖然對結果平常心，「不接受也得接受」，平日也沒有催谷小孩，但亦準備了資料到數間北區學校叩門，若叩門不成功，會讓小孩先入讀青衣區學校，爭取在1年級後轉校，她更不排除跨境搬來香港，專注為小孩安排轉校事宜。<br />\n<br />\n另一內地家長袁先生的兒子則被派到東涌，他坦言不太熟悉東涌，也不認識被派到的學校，對結果感到失望，自己不太會考慮讓兒子入讀，但無論如何會先註冊，之後再叩門，如果不成功，將考慮回深圳報讀國際學校或港人子弟學校。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56777184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56777184&d=Meg8eMkED75wBlDILqO4umMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=303efa3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56777184&h=ca7486f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56777184</a>"},{"pid":"e0b423ba7c548798eaea4040f185812cfa825ab6","tid":268488,"uid":100103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f87737ed5927c507398172feeb30d65d6f53d","tid":268488,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"死撚返狗籠啦"},{"pid":"610799251ce0a4ea4af97dc32629703794be4003","tid":268488,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd8e75b304b319438396f8774c1c76a1646736f2","tid":268488,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:45:51.000Z","msg":"睇下依家既香港<br />\n不知所謂"},{"pid":"292e375608411b360d17b615c88cc521d046c38a","tid":268488,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"有書選仲要嫌三嫌四"},{"pid":"4c4af1c717f115f5df13a21e8bee0283bb30dd15","tid":268488,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036bbd6a88483a0cde9eadf1088c81e8bf5019ba","tid":268488,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"東涌咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a879dda09daf7e5fcf6b92bab839ec18e8b43179","tid":268488,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東涌咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘得過你？"},{"pid":"be9421b00510bda8fe9c2036fb006581b396dae6","tid":268488,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東涌咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘得過你？</blockquote><br />\n你慘d"},{"pid":"a4a3ee40eba24405b55f6498c2e0f17f8bfc6ad9","tid":268488,"uid":48624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"活該活該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgm